.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zG4KX4.gif&h=cb58b099&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbzLLqsZLFPhHRzAQN2Fxptfxaofc6k8KQAd4mBGdJEEd?filename=nohPbC4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnohPbC4.gif&h=37c39188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNS34ZRYK4B6EYtNwbf9N5t3pkumrvTUKZwgznQaYhm3s?filename=p2C1gpy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp2C1gpy.gif&h=6fb8790a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmbgeiay6EDE4cUQLLz2zWDo86jyk8wQfu33aKNfamw8n3?filename=n1mRL6O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1mRL6O.png&h=0ab5d5f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPhGxSibAR4MjoZZ9GdHaa429FpQ1bfgExgJswJtYJnyE?filename=mo8tdQZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmo8tdQZ.png&h=1f9a3365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVHPELJudBujJN3esaCbEpANhz4F89JPi7eFtx79goF9Q?filename=ceTiUhV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceTiUhV.png&h=f4682246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBy哪有大忙人 <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYzPPr1bordMdu1LnCtPwEpPhRQq6669iYKDAwtPP8ijV?filename=B5ewci7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB5ewci7.gif&h=a41dd670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQDEmnfbhi2KotQaRDeGNmtGZSp3aKuKiatqrr8NFrBXa?filename=j7m2YGr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7m2YGr.gif&h=cff041cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNUp4VDjxCg9Fp7bWCqEAY6MVmPcKjKAk6iWtHdvJGa6L?filename=52DpmEX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52DpmEX.png&h=9beb31fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPEXtEctcowqkYwA6JNtXKyW7DRsRKcB6kgLGquT9wNoR?filename=WVzk2jw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVzk2jw.png&h=7ddc8c68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBy黑貓老公 <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX8BXhw1p43Myd1sHJjJuRpSHfpXbkycG1auWu4u6FFMY?filename=EwQULYd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwQULYd.jpg&h=f7c28edf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2397311ebab966dcfab52c87f03c9ac2304c37a","tid":2500966,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:56:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>龍7業後訪談日文原文</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://febri.jp/topics/%e6%8a%95%e7%a8%bf%e3%83%86%e3%82%b9%e3%83%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffebri.jp%2Ftopics%2F%25e6%258a%2595%25e7%25a8%25bf%25e3%2583%2586%25e3%2582%25b9%25e3%2583%2588%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrdE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=730c80a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://febri.jp/topics/%e6%8a%95%e7%a8%bf%e3%83%86%e3%82%b9%e3%83%88/</a><br />\n<br />\nBy 星漾晴<br />\n轉自K島 唔肯定係咪啱 等識日文出黎對<br />\n<br />\n跟之前一樣大概翻了一下訪談內容 <br />\n&gt;上班偷弄囧 <br />\n<br />\n一些內容先前跟粗品的兩場訪談就已經提過了。 <br />\n&gt;這次是為了回報老粉，讓他們重新體驗考察樂趣為起點作的。 <br />\n&gt;原作裡沙都子的成長描寫篇幅被犧牲了，所以這次她是主角。 <br />\n&gt;暮蟬就是暮蟬，跟海貓的關聯當成彩蛋程度就好。 <br />\n<br />\n新的內容 <br />\n-製作組熟知各媒體的暮蟬作品和中心思想。 <br />\n-角色設計的渡邊老師是虎牙+OK繃之神。 <br />\n-除了配沙都子的金井小姐外，聲優們基本上不知道劇情發展， <br />\n尤其是對配梨花的田村小姐更是嚴格保密。 <br />\n-卒播放後回頭審視祟騙篇會有不同看法。 <br />\n-標題合起來的卒業是指這次動畫故事的收尾，和系列完結無關。 <br />\n<br />\n基本上也重申了龍騎士自己的想法，希望觀眾能享受、珍惜 <br />\n大家一起推敲的過程，而不是只視正解為唯一、其他都不重要。 <br />\n尤其是在現今SNS蓬勃發展的時代。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTpADTW2CDwiby3i7QWvkrdSZ9aDAtQQ2W5tDjCVKKS3h?filename=RvAU0SK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvAU0SK.png&h=01a3bb66&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVPNvgopKhXBCzM9bCYN336PPkvjE8TVMg93fu2MZo2Ap?filename=e9Eq7xL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe9Eq7xL.png&h=88bbd8b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5cebe289b00842c20d7f25019f8ee70f90638230","tid":2500966,"uid":83504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vxg2Dp-7roo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fvxg2Dp-7roo&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrdE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=8e6c0a4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vxg2Dp-7roo</a><br />\n卒2nd pv<br />\n<br />\n驚thumbnail劇透所以唔放喺#1啦"},{"pid":"d9317c7227ea599eaac8882a60f86e7f81d24549","tid":2500966,"uid":120302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:58:33.000Z","msg":"[/quote]魔禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇維基得到嘅資訊仲多過睇動畫"},{"pid":"7ce44d2f11f809d819ba8f78492050fca3bedd1b","tid":2500966,"uid":294582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9317c7227ea599eaac8882a60f86e7f81d24549","tid":2500966,"uid":120302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:58:33.000Z","msg":"[/quote]魔禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇維基得到嘅資訊仲多過睇動畫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:59:14.000Z","msg":"講返頭先輕改動畫嘅問題<br />\n我覺得大部份都係太趕<br />\n係原作個節奏先啱口味<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ebc797040724140fbf0294bace224f32e6f818","tid":2500966,"uid":224646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T05:00:25.000Z","msg":"本身鬼滅內容唔係咩新野，而成班人除左睇過下王道漫or從來都未睇過動畫就衝入去睇鬼滅，更加解釋到呢套只係部大眾向嘅戲，極端黎講可以唔納入做新番動畫行列，已經係新海誠/宮崎駿類嘅作品<br />\n<br />\n有追開新番嘅人，大把選擇，冇必要睇大眾向作品<br />\n所以唔係老唔老屎忽問題，係受眾類型問題"},{"pid":"71a1d81e